caption:
🌅✨ “Golden hour, endless horizons.”
Evelyn, auburn hair flowing and sun-kissed skin glowing, stands on a cliff overlooking the turquoise sea. Her off-shoulder cropped dress flutters gently in the breeze as she captures the view with her camera. A local fisherman works nearby, a dog explores the scene, and a drone hovers above, adding cinematic depth to the serene beach and distant mountains. 📸🐾
